#

Hearty Vegan Borscht

60 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A vibrant and nourishing beet soup with a mix of vegetables, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 large, peeled and diced
  • carrots: 2, chopped
  • potato: 1 large, diced
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: to taste
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
